00:35:12,083 --> 00:35:19,083
RANKOSHI STATION

475
00:35:30,375 --> 00:35:32,541
Huh? Is this how you do it?

476
00:35:32,625 --> 00:35:33,833
Hello?

477
00:35:34,541 --> 00:35:36,458
Is it… Oh, this way.

478
00:35:37,291 --> 00:35:38,375
Let's see here…

479
00:35:39,375 --> 00:35:40,375
Hi, Saeko!

480
00:35:41,500 --> 00:35:42,333
Doing well?

481
00:35:44,416 --> 00:35:47,000
That face tells me you're not well.
What's wrong?

482
00:35:47,083 --> 00:35:47,916
What?

483
00:35:50,125 --> 00:35:51,000
Are you walking?

484
00:35:51,500 --> 00:35:52,333
Oh, jeez.

485
00:35:52,958 --> 00:35:54,208
Yeah, I'm walking.

486
00:35:54,791 --> 00:35:56,375
What is this, Hiro?

487
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:57,958
Is something up?

488
00:35:58,041 --> 00:36:03,041
Well, I could sense
that you were feeling a bit blue.

489
00:36:04,583 --> 00:36:05,666
Was I right?

490
00:36:06,166 --> 00:36:07,041
I see.

491
00:36:07,125 --> 00:36:08,666
I was right, huh?

492
00:36:09,208 --> 00:36:12,333
This is what people call a good man.

493
00:36:13,041 --> 00:36:13,875
Right?

494
00:36:16,250 --> 00:36:17,375
Jeez…

495
00:36:19,291 --> 00:36:20,166
Thank you.

496
00:36:24,333 --> 00:36:27,291
When someone I've lost
comes up in my mind,

497
00:36:28,708 --> 00:36:32,541
I think it's because
that person misses me.

498
00:36:34,583 --> 00:36:36,500
That they have come to see me.

499
00:36:39,875 --> 00:36:42,000
My wife's been gone for eight years,

500
00:36:42,791 --> 00:36:46,333
but she comes to see me every day.

501
00:36:47,583 --> 00:36:49,208
She must be crazy about me.

502
00:36:50,541 --> 00:36:51,541
Right?

503
00:36:51,625 --> 00:36:55,041
So, I'm more than happy to have them
appear in my head.

504
00:36:57,833 --> 00:36:59,291
And Saeko…

505
00:36:59,958 --> 00:37:02,666
I know you said it's hard
to look toward the future,

506
00:37:03,375 --> 00:37:04,250
but it's okay.

507
00:37:04,791 --> 00:37:08,875
Unlike cars, humans aren't designed
to walk backward easily.

508
00:37:09,875 --> 00:37:10,708
Right?

509
00:37:11,458 --> 00:37:16,333
So, that means that
if you're walking every single day,

510
00:37:17,041 --> 00:37:18,333
you're moving forward.

511
00:37:19,416 --> 00:37:20,833
You're taking steps forward.

512
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:22,833
Okay?

513
00:37:32,625 --> 00:37:34,333
Follow your heart.

514
00:37:35,333 --> 00:37:36,250
Okay, Saeko?

515
00:37:37,500 --> 00:37:38,333
Okay.

516
00:37:46,125 --> 00:37:48,041
You see that?

517
00:37:52,625 --> 00:37:53,458
Look.

518
00:37:54,250 --> 00:37:55,583
The Hawaiian skies.

519
00:37:56,916 --> 00:37:58,416
I'm sure you'll be fine.

520
00:38:03,458 --> 00:38:07,083
Everything will work out, Saeko.

521
00:38:20,125 --> 00:38:23,583
Memories from the person
who gave me their heart…

522
00:38:26,416 --> 00:38:28,875
are inside of me.

523
00:38:30,458 --> 00:38:32,416
Is that possible?

524
00:38:38,625 --> 00:38:39,875
Medically speaking…

525
00:38:39,958 --> 00:38:42,125
It might not be medically proven,

526
00:38:42,833 --> 00:38:45,375
but similar cases
have been reported, right?

527
00:38:47,166 --> 00:38:48,666
I'm right, aren't I?

528
00:38:57,333 --> 00:38:58,791
My heart…

529
00:39:01,625 --> 00:39:04,333
It has memories that aren't mine.

530
00:39:04,416 --> 00:39:06,000
I can't see it any other way.

531
00:39:09,875 --> 00:39:11,083
What…

532
00:39:13,625 --> 00:39:15,416
does this heart want?

533
00:39:20,500 --> 00:39:21,416
It's like…

534
00:39:25,291 --> 00:39:27,333
When I think about what might happen…

535
00:39:31,583 --> 00:39:32,583
I get scared.

536
00:39:59,625 --> 00:40:01,375
Uncle, let's play!

537
00:40:03,458 --> 00:40:04,375
Sure.

538
00:40:05,500 --> 00:40:06,833
What do you want to play?

539
00:40:08,166 --> 00:40:10,000
-Spinning tops.
-Tops?

540
00:40:10,083 --> 00:40:12,208
There we go. Oh, no!

541
00:40:12,708 --> 00:40:14,958
-Yay! I win!
-You're good.

542
00:40:15,041 --> 00:40:18,083
If I win this one,
you have to do as I say.

543
00:40:18,583 --> 00:40:19,625
What?

544
00:40:19,708 --> 00:40:20,541
Sure.

545
00:40:20,625 --> 00:40:21,750
-Here we go.
